Package ca.ualberta.cmput301w14t08.geochan.models

Class Summary
Comment A comment within a thread of comments.
Favourites This class handles the threads/comments saved by the user as favourite, to be available for later viewing.
GeoLocation Responsible for GeoLocation services for Comment objects
GeoLocationLog This model class handles all operations involved in logging used locations.
LogEntry This is a container class for one GeoLocationLog entry, it contains a String and a geolocation objects.
ThreadComment ThreadComment is a model class that handles all operations of threads in the application.
ThreadList Utility class that stores and manages an arraylist of ThreadComment objects.
